  "text": "Remark 4. The dependency spectrum (P i ) i∈N characterizes the 'effect' of each componentẽ i on the output of the functioñ e. A relevant work can be found in [CITATION_1] where the output correlation of two functions with i.i.d inputs is characterized using the singular values vector of the matrix P",
